defaultIn terms of changes in CEO pay, those charities that paid their CEOs below £100k in 2007 had increased their CEO salary by an average of 38% (or £32,000 
defaultin actual money) by 2012. Those who paid their CEOs above £100k in 2007 had increased their CEO salary by 6% (or £9000) by 2012.
